### =============================================================================
### ATLAS FOOD — AUTH & PROFILE (STATIC EMAIL VERSION)
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

# Ganti email di sini jika ingin mengetes user lain
@email = tester01@mail.com
@password = Password123!
@name = Tester Atlas

# Dynamic Token (Otomatis terisi setelah Login)
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.data.access_token}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.data.refresh_token}}

### =============================================================================
### A. AUTH SECTION
### =============================================================================

### A1. Register New User
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "{{name}}"
}

###

### A2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

### A3. Get My Profile (Protected)
# @name profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### A4. Refresh Token
# @name refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### A5. Get Profile with New Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{refresh.response.body.data.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
